fulltitle: Alex Foster on meeting and playing with Jaco Pastorius
description:
In this video, Alex talks about how he first met Jaco Pastorius and then went on to perform in Jaco's big band and small ensembles.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Saxophonist Alex Foster has recorded and toured with some of the biggest stars in music. With his project, "The Jaco Tribute Band", he pays homage to the legendary bassist and band-leader, Jaco Pastorius, with whom Alex went on two world tours and recorded multiple albums.

The Band Features some of New York City's most in-demand players including Gil Goldstein (piano), Alex Sipiagin (trumpet), Luis Bonilla (trombone), Matt Garrison (Bass), Johnathan Blake (drums), Theo Hill (piano), and Alina Engibaryan (voice).

Check out Alex's Facebook page for more information and updates:

https://www.facebook.com/AlexFosterMusic
